Package soot.jimple.infoflow.android.source.parsers.xml

Class AbstractXMLSourceSinkParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.android.source.parsers.xml.AbstractXMLSourceSinkParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    XMLSourceSinkParser
    public abstract class AbstractXMLSourceSinkParser
extends Object
    Abstract class for all Flowdroid XML parsers. Returns a Set of Methods when calling the function parse. Subclasses may implement parser specifics to different language engines.
    Author:
    Anna-Katharina Wickert, Joern Tillmans, Steven Arzt, Niklas Vogel
